
Do the following until the user chooses to quit the program.

Ask the user if they're converting to Fahrenheit or Celsius.

If "fahrenheit" 
	ask for the degrees in Celsius
	convert it to Fahrenheit by using the formula c = (f-32)/1.8
	print out the result

If "celsius" 
	ask the user for the degrees in Fahrenheit 
	convert it to celsius with the formula f = c*1.8+32
	print out the result

If "quit"
	print out a message indicating the program is quitting
	quit the program

else 
	print out an error message.
 
